In [38]:
temp = []

for i,j in category_url.items():
    soup = bs4.BeautifulSoup(j[1])
    
    for n in soup.find_all('span', attrs={'class':'info_cp'}):
        temp.append(n.text)
        
    for n in soup.find_all('span', attrs={'class': 'info_thumb'}):
        if n.find('a') == None:
            if '\n' in n.text.strip():
                temp.append(n.text.strip('\n')[0])
            elif n.text.strip() =='':
                temp.append(n.find('img',alt=True)['alt'])
            else:
                temp.append(n.text.strip())
print(temp)

In [87]:
for i,j in category_url.items():
    soup = bs4.BeautifulSoup(j[1])
    #언론사 리스트
    temp = []
    
    for n in soup.find_all('span', attrs={'class':'info_cp'}):
        temp.append(n.text)
        
    for n in soup.find_all('span', attrs={'class': 'info_thumb'}):
        if n.find('a') == None:
            if '\n' in n.text.strip():
                temp.append(n.text.strip('\n')[0])
            elif n.text.strip() =='':
                temp.append(n.find('img',alt=True)['alt'])
            else:
                temp.append(n.text.strip())
    j.append(temp)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

plt.figure(figsize=(10,10))

for i in category_url.keys() :
    rank = {}
    
    for j in unique_data :
        rank[j] = 0
    
    for j in category_url[i][5] :
        if i =='메인':
            continue
        rank[j] += 1
        
    x = rank.keys()
    y = rank.values()
    plt.bar(x,y,label=i)
    
plt.xticks(rotation=90)
plt.legend()
plt.title('분야별 언론사 랭킹')
plt.show()

# 전체 랭킹

rank = {}
for i in data:
    if rank.get(i) == None:
        rank[i] = 1
    else:
        rank[i]+=1
        
print(rank)
